{"tid":293432,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"樹大，恆大，開大，i大邊間最勁？","createTime":"2017-06-22T07:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T16:34:27.000Z","uid":48611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"addc310b26b91d85d60edcf69c31053739bbdf4a","tid":293432,"uid":48611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"邊間自我打飛機最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e681d0081375a8a7def93144e3c6ed893752f45","tid":293432,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:20:09.000Z","msg":"4間都咁廢 好難揀得落手"},{"pid":"33e5d63695427a399f02dec64bea2c71f55fea58","tid":293432,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"講打飛機一定係開大"},{"pid":"f8909a16a34dd7432ed9608329d0a49fef7be57a","tid":293432,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"豪大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95e72f472dee1af08c6b9cc132a8da9faab7808","tid":293432,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"恆大完勝"},{"pid":"8abc68eb89c5908144878d8ddb21e0e7e45585ff","tid":293432,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恆大完勝</blockquote><br />\nPound <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cddd371cfc87148f87057d0c32a0f9ce22c396","tid":293432,"uid":48611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>恆大完勝</blockquote><br />\nPound <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMy"},{"pid":"b2359400f0c4a951d924fa7eac7ba7e8f722c0e0","tid":293432,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:20:27.000Z","msg":"開大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb27899afe3821b824c27103b7c5745bf9aaec1b","tid":293432,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/stock2012/1412427928-311547441_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fstock2012%2F1412427928-311547441_n.jpg&h=35b41973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/stock2012/1412427939-145907474_n.jpg?v=1412427940\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fstock2012%2F1412427939-145907474_n.jpg%3Fv%3D1412427940&h=0e52312e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0db856ccb9f3f3896b24b1be7194a7fa34b427f9","tid":293432,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"On9 i大捨我其誰"},{"pid":"2e995df8859a3fbb750cf6f98ed0b5d0087f519b","tid":293432,"uid":101341,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"搭小巴去恆管<br />\n<br />\n是咁的 <br />\n尋日約曬成班以前中學同學出黎聚下舊，食下飯咁<br />\n本來過程都幾輕鬆愉快既 <br />\n但係突然呢，有一個升左恆大既中學同學就提議玩下遊戲咁，廢事咁悶 <br />\n當中有人就提議玩下D數字遊戲啦，計下數咁 <br />\n大家都話好既，當係玩下啦 <br />\n<br />\n咁就一直計啦，突然間有一鋪 <br />\n我唔小心咁將好簡單既加數計錯左，將10+7+9+5，計左做32，比正確答案多左一 <br />\n我D FD就笑我話我咁渣嫁，我都唔好意思咁笑左幾下 <br />\n就係依個時候，讀恆大果個FD就話我:「咁渣嫁，中學生WO。」 <br />\n由於小弟不材，升唔到上大學，要係下年進行自修<br />\n我當時就無聲出，因為知道恆大係一間好勁既新晉大學， <br />\n所以只可以細細聲同佢講番:「唔好意思囉，大學生。」 <br />\n<br />\n但由於我條氣好唔順，所以決定係聽日去佢果間恆大到搵佢再玩過隻GAME <br />\n由於我住九龍果邊，唔係好熟新界﹗路 <br />\n<br />\n上左小巴，途中見到有數棟好有霸氣既建築物，坐立係山與屋村中間，旁邊仲有幾個工地作為點綴，幾個地盤佬企係街邊，左手撩住鼻屎，右手抓下屎忽。 <br />\n<br />\n我心諗，依一間一定就係傳說中既恆大 <br />\n<br />\n由於我坐係車尾。迫使我一定要運用我豪壯既聲音大叫出我既目的地 <br />\n<br />\n「恆大有落唔該。」 <br />\n<br />\n講完之後仲要撥下頭髮，電一電側邊D女 <br />\n諗住可以靠下「恆大」既威名，去型一陣，溝下女<br />\n點知個小巴司機又好大聲咁回應我:「恆咩Q大啊，恆管就有。」 <br />\n係依個時侯，車上引出一陣爆笑 <br />\n坐係我側邊個中學妹都引唔住笑左我一陣 <br />\n<br />\n我都唔等佢停車，即刻係個車窗到跳左出去 <br />\n<br />\n我跑入恆大，即刻搵我個FD對質 <br />\n我問佢:「依間唔係恆大咩?做咩我岩岩落車嗌恆大會被人笑。」 <br />\n我個FD聽到我咁樣講，面都紅埋咁答我:「關唔關你事啊。」"},{"pid":"a8811b94fb9c367b4c44ed611c4b34b166bdbd3c","tid":293432,"uid":93411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f121da307eb1532b787350fbc3c65421f5d5b5b","tid":293432,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"廣州恆大最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4203c8b0532f64326b85dc5b805e3777f2cdc6","tid":293432,"uid":60817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"樹仁勁過三大啱，搵呢幾間比算咩意思先"},{"pid":"7b443598dbfe34eccc888aec49960b82261ce1e7","tid":293432,"uid":60817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樹仁勁過三大喎，搵呢幾間比算咩意思先</blockquote>"}]}